snippet.title: Resident Evil 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
You have once again entered the world of survival horror. Take a trip to Raccoon City with Resident Evil 2 on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and Steam!

For more official news and updates, follow us on:
Twitter - https://twitter.com/RE_Games
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/residentevil/
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/re_games/ 
www.residentevil2.com
